snippet.textDisplay: Hi ! Even as I continue to object to improvisations with the music of Langas & Manganiars, after following you chaps closely, I must say that the level of your instrumentation is unbelievable ! NO DOUBT ! And such a collection of young talent with a variety of 'non-regular' instruments is heart warming ... coz it shows that Indian music is in good hands .. its SAFE ! That the gen-next is acting responsibly towards our rich tradition of music. So THANK YOU for that, at the least.
